%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as VCF Milestone UI
participant BFF as Execution BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant EXE as Execution Service
participant GCS as Governance Consumption Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

PM->>UI: Click VCF milestone
UI->>BFF: Open VCF update view
BFF->>ORCH: Validate VCF milestone behavior
ORCH->>GCS: Get object behavior metadata
GCS-->>ORCH: VCF milestone applicability
ORCH->>EXE: Fetch current VCF milestone state
EXE->>READDB: Query WBS execution / VCF data
READDB-->>EXE: Current VCF data
EXE-->>ORCH: Response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show VCF update form

PM->>UI: Save VCF update
UI->>BFF: Submit VCF update
BFF->>ORCH: Start VCF update flow
ORCH->>EXE: Save VCF execution data
EXE->>PRIMARYDB: Insert/Update VCF execution
PRIMARYDB-->>EXE: Save success
EXE-->>ORCH: Save success
ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish VCFUpdated Event
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show updated milestone state